The Postmaster of Mafdet holds an open commission for a complete navigation survey of the Northern Oasis. The oasis approaches and interior are imperfectly documented, creating routing gaps for caravans operating through the northern desert corridor. Survey every accessible section of the oasis and its approaches and return with a complete route record.
Your Northern Oasis survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority. The route documentation has been incorporated into the northern desert corridor reference files that caravan operators consult before departing the harbor.

